  "body": "### Description\n\nCurrently the command `quarkus create extension` is only able to generate maven templates.\r\n\r\nOther sub commands, as `quarkus create app` and `quarkus create cli`  allow to create a new app template with gradle by adding the parameter `--gradle`\r\n\r\nIt would be desired, if `quarkus create extension` whould be aligned with the other sub commands, resulting in the option to create an extension template with gradle.\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\n_No response_",
